data.description: Quaint townhome community with only 5 double structures on each side of a cul de sac street.  this unit is a 2 bedroom, 2 bath townhome with a single car garage and a great privacy fenced yard with several fruit trees and a very large patio.  the living room and dining room are both quite spacious and there is a lovely sunroom/office which could also be used as a guest room .  There are adequate cabinets in the kitchen and also in the laundry room.  The primary bedroom and bath are both quite large and there is a separate shower and also a garden tub with jets. These townhomes are very nice and functional if one is wanting to downsize or maybe a first home with little yard maintenance as the front yard is cut as part of the annual HOA fee.  Also you're right in the city and just several blocks from downtown Hammond!  Come by and take a look!
